### Base URL — override per environment
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080


### [PF] Product 101A — eligible (value within 500–5000) → 201 Created
POST {{baseUrl}}/operacoes-credito
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idAssociado": 1,
  "valorOperacao": 1000,
  "segmento": "PF",
  "codigoProdutoCredito": "101A",
  "codigoConta": "0123456789"
}

